        <mxCell id="zMDc__jSJ5ZipZstM7X8-85" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SImuless Runtime Core:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;All controllers and filters and estimator are unified as &lt;strong&gt;stateful discrete-time processing modules&lt;/strong&gt;, sharing the same core characteristics: &lt;strong&gt;parameter set, internal state, periodic tick-driven step update, input-to-output signal transformation, and reset/reconfiguration capability&lt;/strong&gt;. Each module executes deterministically at a fixed sampling period, updating its internal state and producing the latest output signal based on current inputs and runtime parameters.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
